 />\n喺我生命入面從此消失我就好傷心<br />\n<br />\n諗起佢有幾衰，有幾多承諾做唔到就覺得分手係啱<br />\n但夜䦨人靜自己一個又好掛住佢，好想佢喺我身邊<br />\n覺得自己好冇用<br />\n比啲理性好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffa5131abba826d97d502fa5916972e67a94958","tid":2274681,"uid":57196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"787acfe579d675e5164b16cf752bf5c5c15fed99","tid":2274681,"uid":210638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca5928d3af3548135477f5d337d15400862729c5","tid":2274681,"uid":57196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b6cb869653619f0c973afe11403886e235a29c12","tid":2274681,"uid":34873,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:59:17.000Z","msg":"由得自己諗啦，諗諗下會發現每日越諗越少，最後就會諗唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"已經24小時無停過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"先24小時<br />\n沒返240都唔好講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"都兩個星期啦，發夢都係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"745255727ea8839cadd743ae051434326ccecac4","tid":2274681,"uid":57196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe70d10a7d14a0c569a3460174aa82374492bd62","tid":2274681,"uid":179906,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"dbd54484054512008f13279c6cfd71083d5d077a","tid":2274681,"uid":227695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a5a0a8fc907f9befb76c42bd53c31974b5a95e3","tid":2274681,"uid":181033,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"係「重要性」嘅問題<br />\n時間沖淡嘅，其實係重要性<br />\n一樣嘢冇左重要性，自然會唔記得<br />\n現實少少講，搵D更緊要嘅嘢佔據自己生活，好快會唔記得"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"慢慢習慣生活無左佢 亦要接受以後都唔會有 （一諗起成世都無左佢就頹到爆）成日都諗會唔會過多幾個月搵佢會理番我 但佢都好愛佢個ex仲一定比我愛佢既程度更深<br />\n習慣左無佢就無sad但都會好掛住 好想佢可以番黎 覺得如果佢可以愛我真係乜都得 <br />\n無信心搵到一個比佢更好